ebel Ali. Well-bred and in the right stable, he looks primed for a strong first-up showing and the market will be an important guide. 9. HADEE MATIKA was well below his best when resuming at Al Ain, beaten a long way, but he’s far better than that and finds a very suitable race here. Expect a sharp improvement. 1. YARMOUK hasn’t been seen since finishing fifth over 1800m at Al Ain in early February. He has shown enough ability to be a top 4 player fresh and must be respected. 11. TAROUK DU LOUP was safely held on debut over 1600m at Al Ain but should take natural improvement from that experience. Include in all top 4 combos to be safe.\",\"runners\":[5,9,1,11],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Racing  and Sports","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,15,9]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,15,9,16]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,15,16,14]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[15,1,11,10]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,15,2]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,9,15]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,10,15,1]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,15,9,4]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"AUB","raceType":"R"}}